lead_paragraph: JANIS--George Gary, 74, passed away May 22. Graduate Tulane Law. NYS Administrative Judge (retired). Survived by brother David and sister Lenore. Funeral service Thursday, May 26 at 1pm at Sharon Gardens. 1/3
